data.description: Lorena ISD Beauty. Well laid out 4 bedroom, 3 bath, 3 car garage on corner lot that is almost half an acre. Fabulous, well maintained home with a wonderful layout to include 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, formal dining room, breakfast area, spacious family room, well laid out kitchen, plus a 3 car garage on larger corner lot. So much natural light in this  fabulous family room with windows across back, built ins, beautiful fireplace, recessed lighting, and gorgeous tiled floors. Each bedroom is large in size with good closet space. Isolated master suite to include patio access, large bathroom with two sink areas, jetted tub, separate shower, 2 closets, and abundant of storage. Open Kitchen with center island, Built in cooktop, oven, microwave, dishwasher, pantry with pull out drawers, spice rack area on island, custom cabinets, and charming breakfast area with windows overlooking the backyard. Additional qualities include laundry room w- built in ironing board, freezer space, desk, and sink, new paint, newer AC on south side of home, 2 hot water heaters, wired for surround sound, and a 3 car garage ( 3rd bay can be used as workshop/gym area). This lovely, warm, well kept home in Lorena ISD sits on .48 of a lot size is ready to move in and priced to sell. Call today for a tour.
